title 2.9.2.2 View Public Menu

actor "Customer" as Customer
participant "DishController" as Controller
participant "IDishService" as IService
participant "DishService" as Service
participant "IDishRepository" as IRepo
participant "DishRepository" as Repo
participant "AuLacDbContext" as Context

autonumber

Customer -> Controller: GET /api/dish/menu\n?PageIndex=0&PageSize=10&SearchTerm=&CategoryId=
activate Controller

Controller -> IService: GetDishesForCustomerAsync(request, cancellationToken)
activate IService

IService -> Service: GetDishesForCustomerAsync(request, cancellationToken)
activate Service

Service -> IRepo: GetDishesForCustomerAsync(request, cancellationToken)
activate IRepo

IRepo -> Repo: GetDishesForCustomerAsync(request, cancellationToken)
activate Repo

Repo -> Context: Query active online dishes\n(Filter: IsActive=true, IsOnline=true, Include Category)
activate Context

Context --> Repo: Return (dishes, totalCount)
deactivate Context

Repo --> IRepo: Return (dishes, totalCount)
deactivate Repo

IRepo --> Service: Return (dishes, totalCount)
deactivate IRepo

Service -> Service: Map dishes to DishDisplayDto list\n(Include first image URL)
Service --> IService: Return (items, totalCount)
deactivate Service

IService --> Controller: Return (items, totalCount)
deactivate IService

Controller -> Controller: Create PagedResult<DishDisplayDto>
Controller -> Controller: Create ApiResponse<PagedResult<DishDisplayDto>>

Controller --> Customer: Return 200 OK with public menu
deactivate Controller

@enduml